race.comment: MIKE ANGELO ZEAL (1) quickly into stride to win over the 400m at Geelong two runs back then raced on speed again when finishing second at this track last start. Rates highly and will give a great sight. JAMES'S ENTITY (7) is having his first look at this circuit. Comes here an impressive winner latest at Geelong in a Grade 5 in one of the quickest times of the program (22.71). Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Should feature again. AMRON BOBBY (2) was prominent early from the tricky draw and did a fair job to be beaten 1.5 lengths into second (22.75) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 400m. Expected to be in this for a long way. WITH THE WIND (6) has claims again if she runs up to the latest effort.
